data.description: Step into the perfect blend of comfort and elegance in the coveted Meridian Campus community. It is nestled at the end of a tranquil cul-de-sac, backing up to the lush greenbelt adjacent to the golf course. The interior boasts 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, featuring a spacious master suite with a luxurious 5-piece bath, complete with a relaxing soaking tub and a generous walk-in closet. Upstairs, discover 3 additional bedrooms and a convenient hall 5-piece bath. The kitchen is a culinary delight, showcasing granite counters, upgraded stainless steel appliances, and a spacious island. Enjoy the warmth of the living room fireplace and the timeless beauty of wood laminate floors. Seller willing to give buyer $2000 credit towards rate buy down.
